Story: Test HTTP POST request to send data to an API

Given:
  api_url: String = "http://httpbin.org/post"
  request_body: String = "test data from CNS"
  response: String = ""
  status: Integer = 0

Step 1 → Send POST request
  Because: Testing HTTP POST functionality
  Effect: HTTP POST to api_url with request_body into response

Step 2 → Display response
  Because: Show what we received
  Effect: Print "Response: {response}"

Step 3 → Display status code
  Because: Check if request was successful
  Then: status becomes HTTP_STATUS
  Effect: Print "Status code: {status}"

End: Return response
  Because: Return the API response
